        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Empowering Local Curriculum Act</strong></p> <p>This bill specifies that nothing in federal education law shall be construed to require the use, teaching, promotion, or recommendation of any academic discipline, program, or activity that holds certain principles related to race or sex.</p>]]>
        </text>
